creator: ケーサンヨーシ
descriptionHtml:
[Outline of the game]
This game aims to capture the dungeon by sending the units you hired to the dungeon.
The strategy is done automatically by the unit itself, so you should wait for the unit to return.
When the unit returns, equip it with the weapon you have and send it back to the dungeon.
By repeatedly strengthening the unit and sending it to the dungeon, you can gradually capture the dungeon.

[Providing materials]
[atorasoft]
Http://atorasoft.blog18.fc2.com/

[Raindropmemory]
http://raindropmemory.deviantart.com/art/Legendora-Icon-Set-118999011

[Maoudamashii]
Http://maoudamashii.jokersounds.com/

[Official Twitter]
@RpgLeft

[Producer Twitter]
@K344Left

[Producer Blog]
Https://boukyakulog.blogspot.com/
descriptionShort: "I will defeat your enemy" This is a simple RPG

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
・We increased the number of members by two.
・The minimum value when absorbing the enemy's H when attacking was set to 1.
・Added 1000 floors to increase / decrease selection of floors.
・Added the current calculation status to the battle history.
